00:01:32,289 --> 00:01:39,830
[Better Halves]

2
00:01:40,250 --> 00:01:42,800
[Episode 20]

3
00:01:43,690 --> 00:01:45,120
[Shi's Mansion]

4
00:01:45,220 --> 00:01:47,350
[Gentle Breeze and Soft Rain]

5
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:53,470
Father, Mother, Xianxian.

6
00:01:54,150 --> 00:01:56,039
Tomorrow, I plan to exchange

7
00:01:56,039 --> 00:01:57,100
Information Cards

8
00:01:57,150 --> 00:01:58,190
for Xianxian and Pan'er

9
00:01:58,190 --> 00:01:59,450
to set the engagement.

10
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:00,730
What do you think?

11
00:02:00,900 --> 00:02:01,700
That's great.

12
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:06,640
It's a wonderful thing.

13
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:09,360
But Xianxian,

14
00:02:09,470 --> 00:02:10,900
you've always been rough,

15
00:02:10,900 --> 00:02:13,130
playing with swords and weapons all day.

16
00:02:13,130 --> 00:02:15,820
From now on,
you must learn to be considerate

17
00:02:16,140 --> 00:02:17,720
and treat Ms. Li well.

18
00:02:17,790 --> 00:02:18,620
Do you hear me?

19
00:02:19,060 --> 00:02:19,990
Mother,

20
00:02:20,220 --> 00:02:21,870
with a good role model like Father,

21
00:02:21,870 --> 00:02:23,680
I'll be a good husband too.

22
00:02:23,970 --> 00:02:25,750
Xianxian, let me tell you.

23
00:02:25,850 --> 00:02:28,590
A true man should be strong and dependable
out in the world,

24
00:02:28,590 --> 00:02:29,350
but at home,

25
00:02:31,340 --> 00:02:32,800
he must know how to bend...

26
00:02:35,270 --> 00:02:36,010
How to bend.

27
00:02:40,770 --> 00:02:42,100
Congratulations, Shi.

28
00:02:42,190 --> 00:02:43,850
Congratulations, Xianxian.

29
00:02:43,940 --> 00:02:45,410
Thank you. Thank you.

30
00:02:46,350 --> 00:02:46,530
[Gentle Breeze and Soft Rain]

31
00:02:46,530 --> 00:02:47,870
Come on. Let's eat.

32
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,470
See her out.

33
00:02:50,490 --> 00:02:51,040
Yes.

34
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:51,800
Take care.

35
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:52,840
This way, Miss.

36
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:56,430
Ke, Mr. Yan, you are here.

37
00:02:56,640 --> 00:02:57,890
Chief is in the study.

38
00:02:57,990 --> 00:02:59,240
Pan'er.

39
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:00,840
I'm not here for him today.

40
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:01,680
I'm here for you.

41
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:02,500
For me?

42
00:03:02,890 --> 00:03:05,520
Do you know what day it is today?

43
00:03:06,630 --> 00:03:08,840
Today's the eighth day of the lunar month.

44
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:10,530
What's so special about it?

45
00:03:10,900 --> 00:03:12,440
Today's the eighth day of the lunar month,

46
00:03:12,440 --> 00:03:14,260
an auspicious day for marriage,
betrothal ceremonies,

47
00:03:14,260 --> 00:03:16,630
engagement discussions,
and business openings.

48
00:03:16,630 --> 00:03:18,510
Shi Xianxian,
the eldest son of the Shi family,

49
00:03:18,510 --> 00:03:20,590
asked me, a marriage broker
from the Official Matchmaking Agency,

50
00:03:20,590 --> 00:03:22,020
to exchange the Information Cards.

51
00:03:22,020 --> 00:03:22,070
[Information Card]

52
00:03:22,070 --> 00:03:23,720
Please accept it, Pan'er.

53
00:03:24,710 --> 00:03:26,760
Pan'er, you know what?

54
00:03:26,950 --> 00:03:27,780
Xianxian was so eager

55
00:03:27,780 --> 00:03:30,910
that he nearly dragged me here
in the middle of the night.

56
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:33,090
[Information Card]

57
00:03:33,550 --> 00:03:35,430
So, Pan'er, let me

58
00:03:35,450 --> 00:03:37,230
take your Information Card home.

59
00:03:37,230 --> 00:03:38,520
Then wait a moment, Ke.

60
00:03:38,670 --> 00:03:40,070
I'll go get it right away.

61
00:03:44,050 --> 00:03:46,650
So... they're officially engaged?

62
00:03:47,260 --> 00:03:49,970
After she gives me her Information Card,

63
00:03:50,070 --> 00:03:51,140
it's settled.

64
00:03:53,150 --> 00:03:54,690
So this is how marriages are arranged
in the capital.

65
00:03:54,690 --> 00:03:55,829
So elaborate.

66
00:03:56,690 --> 00:03:58,100
That's not all.

67
00:03:58,180 --> 00:04:01,270
There're still compatibility assessment,
betrothal ceremony, and date choosing.

68
00:04:01,270 --> 00:04:03,130
Only then can the wedding be held.

69
00:04:03,220 --> 00:04:04,950
Marriage is a major life event.

70
00:04:05,050 --> 00:04:06,730
Not a single step can be skipped.

71
00:04:06,730 --> 00:04:07,900
This way, after marriage,

72
00:04:07,900 --> 00:04:10,160
the couple will cherish each other more.

73
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:13,690
Come on.
I'll show you around Xibao Pavilion.

74
00:04:14,230 --> 00:04:14,730
Let's go.

75
00:04:14,730 --> 00:04:15,360
Let's go.

76
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:24,350
Try it.

77
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:25,830
Smells good, doesn't it?

78
00:04:25,830 --> 00:04:27,030
It smells wonderful.

79
00:04:31,610 --> 00:04:32,150
Ke.

80
00:04:32,700 --> 00:04:33,040
[Information Card]

81
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,300
The Information Card.

82
00:04:34,330 --> 00:04:34,930
Great.

83
00:04:35,050 --> 00:04:36,920
I'll go tell Xianxian the good news now.

84
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:38,520
Pan'er, I wonder what you...

85
00:04:39,110 --> 00:04:41,220
No, no, no, Sister-in-law.

86
00:04:41,580 --> 00:04:43,159
Sister-in-law, I wonder what you

87
00:04:43,159 --> 00:04:44,730
think about the wedding date.

88
00:04:44,730 --> 00:04:46,440
Chief isn't even married yet.

89
00:04:46,470 --> 00:04:48,200
How could I dare go ahead of him?

90
00:04:52,290 --> 00:04:54,970
Ke, since you're here,
why didn't you go upstairs?

91
00:04:54,970 --> 00:04:55,980
Lu.

92
00:04:58,200 --> 00:04:59,350
[Information Card]

93
00:05:01,270 --> 00:05:02,670
At this rate, the Shi family

94
00:05:02,670 --> 00:05:05,470
is going to steal away
everyone in Xibao Pavilion.

95
00:05:05,990 --> 00:05:08,180
It's not like you guys aren't willing.

96
00:05:09,050 --> 00:05:09,780
Alright,

97
00:05:10,090 --> 00:05:11,150
since you're here,

98
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:13,930
invite Mr. Yan upstairs to have a seat.

99
00:05:16,890 --> 00:05:18,330
Then I'll gladly accept your invitation.

100
00:05:18,330 --> 00:05:19,510
Lead the way, Lu.

101
00:05:27,060 --> 00:05:30,320
Every one of these paintings
is full of exquisite meaning.

102
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:32,760
Mr. Lu, you truly have a discerning eye.

103
00:05:33,570 --> 00:05:35,600
Xibao Pavilion
deals in calligraphy and paintings.

104
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:38,000
Naturally, we have many in our collection.

105
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:41,730
Mr. Lu, you have a discerning eye.

106
00:05:42,090 --> 00:05:44,220
I'm lucky to see so many works

107
00:05:44,270 --> 00:05:45,470
of Mr. Lin Yuan today.

108
00:05:45,890 --> 00:05:47,159
It's truly eye-opening.

109
00:05:47,159 --> 00:05:49,290
Mr. Lin Yuan's painting style is free,

110
00:05:49,330 --> 00:05:50,720
always showing something fresh.

111
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:52,409
Even those who know nothing about art

112
00:05:52,409 --> 00:05:53,940
can't help but marvel at it.

113
00:05:54,340 --> 00:05:56,670
Perhaps this is Mr. Lin Yuan's intention—

114
00:05:56,770 --> 00:05:58,800
he hopes his works don't simply end up

115
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:00,610
sealed away in the homes of the noble,

116
00:06:00,610 --> 00:06:02,210
but can be appreciated by all

117
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:04,170
and enter households everywhere.

118
00:06:06,340 --> 00:06:07,380
Lu,

119
00:06:07,780 --> 00:06:09,240
you're so knowledgeable.

120
00:06:12,050 --> 00:06:15,110
His spirit is as high as mountains
and as long as rivers.

121
00:06:17,640 --> 00:06:19,040
When Mr. Lin Yuan paints,

122
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:20,700
he avoids dragging the brush.

123
00:06:20,930 --> 00:06:23,010
He believes
dragging dulls the stroke's power,

124
00:06:23,010 --> 00:06:24,640
makes the work feel restless,

125
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:26,440
and disturbs the viewer's mood.

126
00:06:27,180 --> 00:06:28,010
Mr. Lu

127
00:06:28,370 --> 00:06:30,980
understands
Mr. Lin Yuan's thoughts so well.

128
00:06:33,890 --> 00:06:34,870
Mr. Lu,

129
00:06:35,200 --> 00:06:37,450
are you also skilled
in calligraphy and painting?

130
00:06:37,450 --> 00:06:39,120
Might I have the honor today

131
00:06:39,280 --> 00:06:40,970
of seeing your work?

132
00:06:46,900 --> 00:06:49,110
I just completed a piece earlier today.

133
00:06:49,860 --> 00:06:52,930
Ke, Mr. Yan, I'd be honored
if you could offer your insights.

134
00:06:52,930 --> 00:06:54,740
Then lead the way, Lu.

135
00:07:04,230 --> 00:07:07,070
The handwriting... looks so familiar.

136
00:07:07,630 --> 00:07:08,420
Mr. Lu,

137
00:07:08,990 --> 00:07:11,190
is this the painting you just finished?

138
00:07:11,210 --> 00:07:11,820
Yes.

139
00:07:24,760 --> 00:07:25,580
Ke.

140
00:07:25,750 --> 00:07:28,210
This is clearly
Mr. Lin Yuan's handwriting.

141
00:07:28,460 --> 00:07:30,750
Impossible. Lu painted this.

142
00:07:31,090 --> 00:07:33,260
The handwriting may look similar,

143
00:07:33,290 --> 00:07:35,560
but there are still differences.

144
00:07:35,580 --> 00:07:37,710
And this is better than Mr. Lin Yuan's.

145
00:07:41,490 --> 00:07:42,290
Mr. Lu,

146
00:07:42,810 --> 00:07:44,340
you're Mr. Lin Yuan, right?

147
00:07:49,270 --> 00:07:50,090
No.

148
00:07:51,330 --> 00:07:53,130
What makes you say that, Mr. Yan?

149
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:54,730
The handwriting in this painting

150
00:07:54,730 --> 00:07:56,040
is identical

151
00:07:56,070 --> 00:07:57,350
to Mr. Lin Yuan's.

152
00:07:57,390 --> 00:07:58,900
I couldn't possibly be mistaken.

153
00:07:58,900 --> 00:08:00,360
You are mistaken, Mr. Yan.

154
00:08:00,700 --> 00:08:02,140
I am not Mr. Lin Yuan,

155
00:08:02,890 --> 00:08:04,190
nor do I know him.

156
00:08:06,570 --> 00:08:09,180
How could Lu be Mr. Lin Yuan?

157
00:08:13,010 --> 00:08:13,980
Lu,

158
00:08:14,300 --> 00:08:16,170
are you really not Mr. Lin Yuan?

159
00:08:16,190 --> 00:08:16,870
Ke,

160
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:18,890
I am certainly not Mr. Lin Yuan.

161
00:08:19,170 --> 00:08:21,150
Do you remember when we first met,

162
00:08:21,960 --> 00:08:23,190
you were with me admiring

163
00:08:23,190 --> 00:08:24,650
Mr. Lin Yuan's paintings?

164
00:08:28,350 --> 00:08:29,260
Mr. Yan,

165
00:08:29,710 --> 00:08:31,670
Lu said he's not Mr. Lin Yuan.

166
00:08:31,690 --> 00:08:33,220
So he definitely isn't Mr. Lin Yuan.

167
00:08:33,220 --> 00:08:35,650
Lu and I will help you find him.

168
00:08:36,010 --> 00:08:37,340
You won't be able to find him.

169
00:08:37,340 --> 00:08:38,740
Don't waste your energy.

170
00:08:39,429 --> 00:08:41,690
How could we not find someone who exists?

171
00:08:41,690 --> 00:08:42,289
Unless...

172
00:08:42,309 --> 00:08:43,710
Unless you are Mr. Lin Yuan.

173
00:08:43,710 --> 00:08:44,580
I'm not.

174
00:08:48,510 --> 00:08:50,770
Why do you insist on finding Mr. Lin Yuan?

175
00:08:50,910 --> 00:08:52,440
Because I want to marry him.

176
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:57,090
But...

177
00:08:57,510 --> 00:08:59,080
Mr. Lin Yuan is a man.

178
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:20,000
Qiyue, why did you...

179
00:09:21,890 --> 00:09:22,830
Ke.

180
00:09:22,950 --> 00:09:25,150
Thank you for keeping my secret before.

181
00:09:26,030 --> 00:09:29,030
I know true friends are hard to find.

182
00:09:29,030 --> 00:09:30,510
Everything must begin with honesty.

183
00:09:30,510 --> 00:09:32,350
So I had to reveal my identity.

184
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:35,680
But... but I'm really not Mr. Lin Yuan.

185
00:09:39,850 --> 00:09:40,690
Qiyue,

186
00:09:41,060 --> 00:09:42,750
let's go get changed first.

187
00:09:42,780 --> 00:09:44,480
Lu, we'll talk another day.

188
00:09:44,750 --> 00:09:45,530
Let's go.

189
00:09:45,640 --> 00:09:46,460
Come on.

190
00:09:51,780 --> 00:09:53,670
[Shi's Mansion]

191
00:10:00,180 --> 00:10:00,920
Ke.

192
00:10:01,950 --> 00:10:02,590
Qiyue.

193
00:10:04,230 --> 00:10:05,230
You go first.

194
00:10:08,610 --> 00:10:10,280
Alright, I'll go first.

195
00:10:10,710 --> 00:10:11,610
Qiyue,

196
00:10:11,690 --> 00:10:12,470
do you really think

197
00:10:12,470 --> 00:10:14,010
Lu is Mr. Lin Yuan?

198
00:10:19,820 --> 00:10:20,970
I believe he is.

199
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:23,510
Qiyue, you think Lu is Mr. Lin Yuan

200
00:10:23,530 --> 00:10:25,320
just because of one painting.

201
00:10:25,350 --> 00:10:26,740
Isn't that too hasty?

202
00:10:26,870 --> 00:10:29,290
Besides, for a master like Mr. Lin Yuan,

203
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:31,510
there're plenty of people
who copy his style.

204
00:10:31,510 --> 00:10:33,170
You've only seen a few of his works,

205
00:10:33,170 --> 00:10:35,000
and you don't know
what kind of person he is.

206
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:36,950
Ke, trust me.

207
00:10:37,020 --> 00:10:38,460
He must be Mr. Lin Yuan.

208
00:10:38,600 --> 00:10:39,980
You promised me before.

209
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:41,450
If I can find Mr. Lin Yuan,

210
00:10:41,470 --> 00:10:43,190
that means we're destined to meet.

211
00:10:43,190 --> 00:10:44,670
You said you would help me.

212
00:10:44,890 --> 00:10:45,650
Right?

213
00:10:46,260 --> 00:10:49,270
Qiyue, I did say that.

214
00:10:49,290 --> 00:10:51,170
Ke, I know

215
00:10:51,640 --> 00:10:53,920
Mr. Lu is the one you love.

216
00:10:54,270 --> 00:10:56,230
But I've traveled so far to the capital

217
00:10:56,230 --> 00:10:57,910
just to find Mr. Lin Yuan.

218
00:10:58,550 --> 00:10:59,650
Before, he didn't know

219
00:10:59,650 --> 00:11:02,210
someone has been quietly admiring him.

220
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:03,240
Now that he knows,

221
00:11:03,250 --> 00:11:05,440
you should give him a chance to choose,

222
00:11:05,650 --> 00:11:07,650
and give me a chance to fight for him.

223
00:11:26,580 --> 00:11:27,950
Xianxian, Chongshan.

224
00:11:29,230 --> 00:11:31,980
Ke, the weather is nice today.

225
00:11:32,030 --> 00:11:33,480
How about we take you out for a walk?

226
00:11:33,480 --> 00:11:35,360
Let's... go to the snack street.

227
00:11:37,160 --> 00:11:38,440
I don't want to go.

228
00:11:40,590 --> 00:11:41,690
[Ruyi Rolls: 15 boxes
Peach Kernel Crisps: 10 boxes]

229
00:11:42,120 --> 00:11:43,150
Ke.

230
00:11:43,170 --> 00:11:45,460
You're... holding it upside down.

231
00:11:45,590 --> 00:11:46,150
Here.

232
00:11:50,780 --> 00:11:54,090
I... I was reading it upside down
for inspiration.

233
00:11:59,610 --> 00:12:00,490
[Ruyi Rolls: 15 boxes
Peach Kernel Crisps: 10 boxes]

234
00:12:01,050 --> 00:12:03,690
Ke, if something's troubling you,

235
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:04,740
you can tell me.

236
00:12:05,510 --> 00:12:06,410
That's right.

237
00:12:06,430 --> 00:12:08,360
Whatever it is, I've got your back.

238
00:12:08,580 --> 00:12:10,440
Thank you, Xianxian, Chongshan.

239
00:12:11,020 --> 00:12:13,290
I am facing a difficult problem.

240
00:12:13,310 --> 00:12:16,500
What could possibly be too difficult
for our Ke?

241
00:12:16,530 --> 00:12:17,060
Right?

242
00:12:17,100 --> 00:12:17,630
Yes.

243
00:12:17,920 --> 00:12:18,980
If—

244
00:12:19,160 --> 00:12:20,340
I mean if

245
00:12:20,990 --> 00:12:23,560
you two were in love with the same girl,

246
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:24,600
what would you do?

247
00:12:26,550 --> 00:12:28,270
-That's impossible.
-That's impossible.

248
00:12:28,270 --> 00:12:30,690
No, no, what I meant is...

249
00:12:30,730 --> 00:12:33,880
my good friend and I are in love
with the same person,

250
00:12:34,300 --> 00:12:35,490
what should I do?

251
00:12:35,520 --> 00:12:36,720
That's not possible.

252
00:12:37,240 --> 00:12:38,130
Which good friend?

253
00:12:38,130 --> 00:12:39,230
In love with whom?

254
00:12:45,670 --> 00:12:46,450
Forget it.

255
00:12:47,490 --> 00:12:49,980
Xianxian, Chongshan, I'm leaving.

256
00:12:56,670 --> 00:12:57,390
This is bad.

257
00:12:57,390 --> 00:12:59,890
Who else loves Lu Chi too?

258
00:13:00,010 --> 00:13:02,450
Should we tell him?

259
00:13:02,810 --> 00:13:04,050
Pan'er told me

260
00:13:04,290 --> 00:13:06,200
Chief Lu is her family.

261
00:13:06,390 --> 00:13:07,180
In that case,

262
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:09,000
we're all going to be family then.

263
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:09,360
We should tell him.

264
00:13:09,360 --> 00:13:09,990
Right?

265
00:13:10,120 --> 00:13:11,050
We must tell him.

266
00:13:11,370 --> 00:13:12,500
Let's go to Xibao Pavilion.

267
00:13:12,500 --> 00:13:13,030
Let's go.

268
00:13:25,010 --> 00:13:25,630
Xianxian.

269
00:13:26,780 --> 00:13:27,510
Chongshan.

270
00:13:27,540 --> 00:13:29,940
What brings you to Xibao Pavilion today?

271
00:13:30,680 --> 00:13:33,460
Lu Chi, you're in trouble.

272
00:13:34,190 --> 00:13:35,590
What happened to Ke?

273
00:13:35,800 --> 00:13:36,790
It's not Ke.

274
00:13:36,820 --> 00:13:37,730
It's you.

275
00:13:38,370 --> 00:13:39,050
Me?

276
00:13:39,250 --> 00:13:42,010
One of Ke's close friends loves you.

277
00:13:43,570 --> 00:13:45,860
Ke is pretty upset about it.

278
00:13:47,320 --> 00:13:49,270
Thank you both for coming to tell me.

279
00:13:49,270 --> 00:13:51,600
But there must be some misunderstanding.

280
00:13:52,280 --> 00:13:53,790
I will handle this matter properly

281
00:13:53,790 --> 00:13:55,990
and won't let Ke be troubled by it again.

282
00:13:59,050 --> 00:13:59,880
Of course,

283
00:14:00,170 --> 00:14:01,530
we trust you.

284
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:04,900
We just hope you can handle this well.

285
00:14:05,370 --> 00:14:06,830
We hope you handle it well.

286
00:14:15,510 --> 00:14:16,440
Lu.

287
00:14:16,890 --> 00:14:18,320
Mr. Lin Yuan.

288
00:14:18,940 --> 00:14:19,720
Qiyue.

289
00:14:22,840 --> 00:14:24,300
What should I do?

290
00:14:26,760 --> 00:14:27,860
Don't look at me.

291
00:14:28,800 --> 00:14:30,940
I look awful when I cry.

292
00:14:31,510 --> 00:14:32,540
No, you don't.

293
00:14:33,210 --> 00:14:34,880
I think you're the most beautiful person,

294
00:14:34,880 --> 00:14:36,190
and the one I love most.

295
00:14:36,890 --> 00:14:38,290
I will always protect you

296
00:14:38,360 --> 00:14:39,820
and never let you get hurt.

297
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:41,670
No.

298
00:14:42,930 --> 00:14:45,040
Whether Lu is Mr. Lin Yuan or not,

299
00:14:45,070 --> 00:14:46,780
I will never give him up.

300
00:15:09,260 --> 00:15:10,670
Why did you come?

301
00:15:10,810 --> 00:15:12,340
I came because I missed you.

302
00:15:13,860 --> 00:15:16,190
But there's someone else missing you now.

303
00:15:16,360 --> 00:15:17,230
Ke,

304
00:15:17,450 --> 00:15:18,980
I'm really not Mr. Lin Yuan.

305
00:15:20,490 --> 00:15:21,910
Whether I am or not,

306
00:15:22,220 --> 00:15:24,370
you're the only one I think of and love.

307
00:15:30,930 --> 00:15:33,910
Lu, I believe you.

308
00:15:34,520 --> 00:15:36,110
I won't give you up.

309
00:15:36,910 --> 00:15:37,760
But...

310
00:15:38,180 --> 00:15:39,870
Qiyue won't give up

311
00:15:39,950 --> 00:15:41,800
until she finds Mr. Lin Yuan.

312
00:15:42,070 --> 00:15:43,630
And I don't want to entrust Qiyue

313
00:15:43,630 --> 00:15:45,440
to a complete stranger.

314
00:15:45,810 --> 00:15:48,090
Ke, in my opinion,

315
00:15:48,110 --> 00:15:50,790
Miss Qiyue
doesn't truly love Mr. Lin Yuan.

316
00:15:51,150 --> 00:15:53,290
Although my handwriting is similar to his,

317
00:15:53,290 --> 00:15:55,510
if you look closely,
the differences are obvious.

318
00:15:55,510 --> 00:15:57,170
If she can't even notice that,

319
00:15:57,530 --> 00:15:59,130
how can she claim to love him?

320
00:16:00,590 --> 00:16:01,800
Handwriting?

321
00:16:04,530 --> 00:16:05,280
Yes.

322
00:16:05,880 --> 00:16:07,080
I've got an idea.

323
00:16:13,750 --> 00:16:15,650
Ke, what are you doing?

324
00:16:16,120 --> 00:16:17,580
Appreciating paintings.

325
00:16:26,940 --> 00:16:27,840
Ke,

326
00:16:27,870 --> 00:16:28,750
where did you get

327
00:16:28,750 --> 00:16:30,550
so many new works by Mr. Lin Yuan?

328
00:16:30,550 --> 00:16:33,770
Are you sure
they're all Mr. Lin Yuan's works?

329
00:16:34,670 --> 00:16:36,070
They are all Mr. Lin Yuan's works.

330
00:16:36,070 --> 00:16:36,980
There's no way I'd mistake

331
00:16:36,980 --> 00:16:37,190
[Painted in the Wuxu month
of the Xinchou year]

332
00:16:37,190 --> 00:16:37,710
Mr. Lin Yuan's handwriting.

333
00:16:37,710 --> 00:16:38,490
[Painted in the Dingsi month
of the Xinchou year]

334
00:16:38,580 --> 00:16:41,320
All the five paintings are his works.

335
00:16:46,750 --> 00:16:47,490
Look at this.

336
00:16:50,080 --> 00:16:50,580
[Jiang Yong]

337
00:16:50,760 --> 00:16:51,760
[Qian He]

338
00:16:52,080 --> 00:16:52,700
[Wu Qi]

339
00:16:56,020 --> 00:16:56,720
This...

340
00:16:56,740 --> 00:16:58,150
None of these five paintings

341
00:16:58,150 --> 00:17:00,310
is an authentic work by Mr. Lin Yuan.

342
00:17:00,340 --> 00:17:01,400
I don't believe it.

343
00:17:03,600 --> 00:17:03,780
[Painted in the Wuchen month
of the Jiawu year]

344
00:17:03,780 --> 00:17:05,109
If you don't believe me,

345
00:17:05,750 --> 00:17:06,810
take a look at this.

346
00:17:10,550 --> 00:17:12,490
[Painted in the Wuchen month
of the Jiawu year]

347
00:17:13,099 --> 00:17:14,420
Lu is so impressive.

348
00:17:14,630 --> 00:17:16,190
He painted this himself,

349
00:17:16,480 --> 00:17:18,190
yet Qiyue can't tell at all.

350
00:17:19,119 --> 00:17:20,319
How could this be?

351
00:17:24,040 --> 00:17:24,800
Qiyue,

352
00:17:25,569 --> 00:17:27,310
you say you love Mr. Lin Yuan,

353
00:17:27,710 --> 00:17:29,990
but you can't even tell

354
00:17:30,010 --> 00:17:31,150
if these are originals or imitations.

355
00:17:31,150 --> 00:17:32,370
I don't know why

356
00:17:32,400 --> 00:17:33,830
you're showing me these imitations

357
00:17:33,830 --> 00:17:34,740
today.

358
00:17:35,000 --> 00:17:36,200
If you're trying to deny

359
00:17:36,200 --> 00:17:38,130
my feelings for Mr. Lin Yuan this way,

360
00:17:38,130 --> 00:17:39,160
that's not fair.

361
00:17:39,350 --> 00:17:40,090
Qiyue,

362
00:17:41,200 --> 00:17:42,640
paintings can be similar.

363
00:17:42,640 --> 00:17:43,800
But your ideal match

364
00:17:43,830 --> 00:17:45,170
should be one of a kind.

365
00:17:45,910 --> 00:17:46,970
The person you love

366
00:17:47,070 --> 00:17:48,480
should be genuine,

367
00:17:48,510 --> 00:17:50,040
not just a celebrated name.

368
00:17:50,540 --> 00:17:53,250
If you want to marry someone

369
00:17:53,270 --> 00:17:54,230
just because you like his paintings,

370
00:17:54,230 --> 00:17:55,430
that's not rational.

371
00:17:55,800 --> 00:17:58,610
What if he's not like what you imagine?

372
00:18:02,380 --> 00:18:06,180
Are you sure
you love Mr. Lin Yuan himself,

373
00:18:07,040 --> 00:18:08,930
not the version you've imagined?

374
00:18:14,260 --> 00:18:14,940
Qiyue,

375
00:18:15,770 --> 00:18:17,740
you've seen Lu many times,

376
00:18:18,200 --> 00:18:21,000
but you've never had
any special feelings for him.

377
00:18:21,070 --> 00:18:22,210
Do you really think

378
00:18:22,640 --> 00:18:24,140
he's the same as the Mr. Lin Yuan

379
00:18:24,140 --> 00:18:25,140
you've imagined?

380
00:18:25,270 --> 00:18:27,820
Do you truly want to marry Lu Chi?

381
00:18:33,820 --> 00:18:36,970
Indeed, I don't have any feelings for him.

382
00:18:37,720 --> 00:18:39,960
But when you found out
he was Mr. Lin Yuan,

383
00:18:39,960 --> 00:18:41,820
you said you wanted to marry Mr. Lin Yuan,

384
00:18:41,820 --> 00:18:43,050
not Lu Chi.

385
00:18:43,070 --> 00:18:45,540
Exactly, I want to marry Mr. Lin Yuan.

386
00:18:45,660 --> 00:18:47,150
You don't even know this person.

387
00:18:47,150 --> 00:18:48,740
And you've never spent time with him.

388
00:18:48,740 --> 00:18:50,570
How can you be sure he's the one you love

389
00:18:50,570 --> 00:18:51,640
or want to marry?

390
00:18:53,300 --> 00:18:56,460
Do you plan to spend your life

391
00:18:56,560 --> 00:18:58,360
with his paintings and his name?

392
00:19:01,890 --> 00:19:05,460
Ke, what you said makes sense.

393
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:07,780
Perhaps I really should think

394
00:19:08,130 --> 00:19:09,690
about what I truly want.

395
00:19:12,450 --> 00:19:13,280
It's okay.

396
00:19:13,950 --> 00:19:15,480
Don't rush, take your time.

397
00:19:16,320 --> 00:19:17,350
I promised you

398
00:19:17,940 --> 00:19:19,610
I'd help you find a good match.

399
00:19:19,990 --> 00:19:20,750
Don't worry.

400
00:19:26,320 --> 00:19:27,830
[Marquis Wu'an's Mansion]

401
00:19:36,570 --> 00:19:37,160
My Lord.

402
00:19:40,680 --> 00:19:41,350
My Lord.

403
00:19:42,370 --> 00:19:43,560
Why do you insist on buying

404
00:19:43,560 --> 00:19:45,820
Mr. Lin Yuan's paintings at high prices?

405
00:19:46,040 --> 00:19:47,890
We're already short of money,

406
00:19:48,010 --> 00:19:50,240
and this just makes matters worse.

407
00:19:51,440 --> 00:19:52,780
I have my reasons.

408
00:19:55,050 --> 00:19:57,450
My Lord, now that Ms. Fang has left,

409
00:19:57,650 --> 00:19:59,480
who else
at the Official Matchmaking Agency

410
00:19:59,480 --> 00:20:01,610
can help you marry Gaoyou's princess?

411
00:20:03,090 --> 00:20:03,890
You...

412
00:20:03,910 --> 00:20:05,110
What am I supposed to say about you?

413
00:20:05,110 --> 00:20:06,150
That head of yours

414
00:20:06,180 --> 00:20:07,660
is worse than a decoration!

415
00:20:07,660 --> 00:20:08,320
Idiot!

416
00:20:08,340 --> 00:20:09,400
Yes, you're right.

417
00:20:19,350 --> 00:20:20,100
Master.

418
00:20:23,530 --> 00:20:25,200
Has Marquis Wu'an made any move lately?

419
00:20:25,200 --> 00:20:26,490
So far, nothing.

420
00:20:26,650 --> 00:20:27,700
He's been unusually quiet.

421
00:20:27,700 --> 00:20:28,970
We must not let our guard down.

422
00:20:28,970 --> 00:20:30,000
The calmer it seems,

423
00:20:30,000 --> 00:20:31,570
the more likely
there are hidden undercurrents.

424
00:20:31,570 --> 00:20:32,820
Master, rest assured.

425
00:20:32,820 --> 00:20:34,220
We're all staying alert.

426
00:20:34,550 --> 00:20:36,680
But recently, someone has been buying

427
00:20:36,680 --> 00:20:38,300
Mr. Lin Yuan's paintings at high prices.

428
00:20:38,300 --> 00:20:39,550
Is that suspicious?

429
00:20:41,550 --> 00:20:43,480
I suppose it must be Miss Yan again.

430
00:20:44,950 --> 00:20:45,610
Ignore her.

431
00:20:46,890 --> 00:20:47,950
By the way, Master,

432
00:20:48,050 --> 00:20:49,380
there's one more thing.

433
00:20:49,510 --> 00:20:53,170
His Majesty has been departing the palace
frequently these days.

434
00:21:02,020 --> 00:21:02,910
Miss Qiyue.

435
00:21:05,290 --> 00:21:06,120
Mr. Huang.

436
00:21:09,440 --> 00:21:10,110
Would you like to try this?

437
00:21:10,110 --> 00:21:10,590
Yes.

438
00:21:11,000 --> 00:21:12,400
-It smells so good.
-Sir.

439
00:21:13,880 --> 00:21:14,540
Here you go.

440
00:21:20,960 --> 00:21:21,580
Wait.

441
00:21:22,190 --> 00:21:22,850
Eat slowly.

442
00:21:50,130 --> 00:21:51,790
Mr. Huang, this is far enough.

443
00:22:11,440 --> 00:22:12,530
Kexian, let me do it.

444
00:22:12,530 --> 00:22:13,930
Chongshan, you're here.

445
00:22:17,650 --> 00:22:19,290
[He's Bakery]

446
00:22:19,290 --> 00:22:20,100
Kexian.

447
00:22:20,400 --> 00:22:21,160
Ketian.

448
00:22:23,280 --> 00:22:25,680
Kexian, it's fine.
Go ahead with your work.

449
00:22:27,940 --> 00:22:28,610
Okay.

450
00:22:32,780 --> 00:22:35,110
Chongshan, please come in and have a seat.

451
00:22:43,480 --> 00:22:44,070
Sit.

452
00:22:50,410 --> 00:22:51,290
Thank you.

453
00:22:54,250 --> 00:22:55,010
Ketian.

454
00:22:55,900 --> 00:22:59,010
How have you been lately?

455
00:23:00,120 --> 00:23:01,390
I've been fine.

456
00:23:02,260 --> 00:23:03,720
How about you, Chongshan?

457
00:23:06,770 --> 00:23:10,460
I've been having trouble
sleeping at night recently.

458
00:23:10,790 --> 00:23:12,790
What's wrong? Are you sick?

459
00:23:15,070 --> 00:23:16,890
Indeed, I haven't been feeling right.

460
00:23:16,890 --> 00:23:18,480
I haven't seen you for a few days.

461
00:23:18,480 --> 00:23:20,410
That's what has been troubling me.

462
00:23:23,320 --> 00:23:24,880
Well, now you've seen me.

463
00:23:27,910 --> 00:23:30,240
Try these new desserts made by my brother.

464
00:23:31,430 --> 00:23:32,140
Okay.

465
00:23:40,400 --> 00:23:42,200
It's been a while since I saw Ke.

466
00:23:42,220 --> 00:23:44,750
Has she been busy
with new matchmaking cases?

467
00:23:45,590 --> 00:23:46,200
No.

468
00:23:46,660 --> 00:23:49,510
She and Lu Chi
have been having some issues lately.

469
00:23:50,510 --> 00:23:52,910
Xianxian and I
have been worrying about it.

470
00:23:53,480 --> 00:23:56,000
You're worried about Mr. Lu now?

471
00:23:56,720 --> 00:23:59,050
I thought
you used to dislike him the most.

472
00:24:00,350 --> 00:24:02,610
Indeed, I didn't really like him before.

473
00:24:03,800 --> 00:24:06,120
I thought he was just some man
with no background,

474
00:24:06,120 --> 00:24:08,690
yet he had the nerve to crave for Ke.

475
00:24:09,370 --> 00:24:12,500
But later, I started to feel he's not bad.

476
00:24:12,560 --> 00:24:13,820
He's responsible.

477
00:24:14,450 --> 00:24:15,980
Entrusting Ke to him

478
00:24:16,000 --> 00:24:17,200
makes me feel at ease.

479
00:24:20,380 --> 00:24:22,380
You've eaten enough. Please leave.

480
00:24:23,310 --> 00:24:24,020
Ketian,

481
00:24:25,310 --> 00:24:26,350
why are you suddenly...

482
00:24:26,350 --> 00:24:27,420
Leave. Just leave!

483
00:24:27,590 --> 00:24:29,240
Since you've accepted him
as your future brother-in-law,

484
00:24:29,240 --> 00:24:31,340
go eat desserts at Xibao Pavilion
from now on.

485
00:24:31,340 --> 00:24:32,850
I haven't. Lu Chi...

486
00:24:46,550 --> 00:24:47,680
Where's Chongshan?

487
00:24:49,740 --> 00:24:50,670
He left already?

488
00:24:55,330 --> 00:24:56,610
What just happened?

489
00:24:58,550 --> 00:25:01,480
Kexian, why don't you
go confess your feelings to Ke?

490
00:25:03,920 --> 00:25:05,650
That heartless Shi Chongshan—

491
00:25:05,790 --> 00:25:06,970
he's taken Lu Chi's side.

492
00:25:06,970 --> 00:25:08,970
He actually thinks Lu Chi is better.

493
00:25:16,200 --> 00:25:16,750
Ketian.

494
00:25:18,500 --> 00:25:19,730
I think Chongshan...

495
00:25:20,260 --> 00:25:21,870
is someone you can rely on.

496
00:25:23,340 --> 00:25:25,400
No matter what happens between Ke and me,

497
00:25:25,400 --> 00:25:26,930
you two must get along well.

498
00:25:27,310 --> 00:25:28,910
Don't fall out because of me.

499
00:25:31,510 --> 00:25:34,390
Kexian, you're my only family.

500
00:25:34,590 --> 00:25:35,680
I've made up my mind:

501
00:25:35,680 --> 00:25:37,480
until you find your happiness,

502
00:25:37,550 --> 00:25:38,680
I won't get married.

503
00:25:38,790 --> 00:25:39,790
That's nonsense.

504
00:25:40,770 --> 00:25:43,050
You shouldn't sacrifice your happiness
because of me.

505
00:25:43,050 --> 00:25:44,850
Your happiness is my happiness.

506
00:25:50,850 --> 00:25:53,120
So you plan to give Ke up?

507
00:25:54,360 --> 00:25:56,090
Maybe I'm just not good enough.

508
00:25:56,750 --> 00:25:59,100
So you're discouraged? Want to give up?

509
00:26:01,240 --> 00:26:02,440
My brother

510
00:26:02,750 --> 00:26:05,270
has been voted
as the capital's most eligible bachelor

511
00:26:05,270 --> 00:26:07,050
many times.

512
00:26:07,200 --> 00:26:09,200
You're not inferior to Lu Chi at all.

513
00:26:09,720 --> 00:26:13,010
You're gentle, kind, and thoughtful.

514
00:26:13,110 --> 00:26:14,250
You understand Ke,

515
00:26:14,480 --> 00:26:15,510
tolerate her,

516
00:26:15,640 --> 00:26:17,440
and even indulge her sometimes.

517
00:26:17,790 --> 00:26:19,490
I've seen it all.

518
00:26:20,480 --> 00:26:21,440
In my opinion,

519
00:26:21,480 --> 00:26:23,360
you're the most suited for her.

520
00:26:24,000 --> 00:26:24,620
But

521
00:26:24,720 --> 00:26:26,900
you need to let her know how you feel.

522
00:26:31,020 --> 00:26:31,920
But would Ke

523
00:26:33,320 --> 00:26:34,370
feel the same way?

524
00:26:36,290 --> 00:26:37,700
How Ke feels,

525
00:26:37,730 --> 00:26:38,700
whether she likes you or not—

526
00:26:38,700 --> 00:26:39,900
that's her business.

527
00:26:40,990 --> 00:26:41,760
Kexian,

528
00:26:41,880 --> 00:26:44,070
you should at least try one last time.

529
00:26:44,460 --> 00:26:46,460
Don't leave yourself with regrets.

530
00:26:48,030 --> 00:26:49,300
If it doesn't work out,

531
00:26:49,990 --> 00:26:51,360
we can work on

532
00:26:51,380 --> 00:26:52,380
her parents.

533
00:26:53,270 --> 00:26:54,650
If it works out,

534
00:26:56,110 --> 00:27:00,180
we'll be even closer as family.

535
00:27:08,830 --> 00:27:09,350
Okay.

536
00:27:10,850 --> 00:27:12,110
I'll try one more time.

537
00:27:17,770 --> 00:27:19,940
[Shi's Mansion]

538
00:27:25,720 --> 00:27:26,190
Come.

539
00:27:28,370 --> 00:27:29,370
Kexian, Ketian.

540
00:27:29,390 --> 00:27:30,210
You're here.

541
00:27:30,440 --> 00:27:32,030
-Uncle, Aunt.
-Uncle, Aunt.

542
00:27:32,030 --> 00:27:32,830
-Xianxian, Chongshan.
-Xianxian, Chongshan.

543
00:27:32,830 --> 00:27:33,370
Come.

544
00:27:33,390 --> 00:27:34,260
-Qin'er.
-Sit.

545
00:27:34,290 --> 00:27:35,050
Sit.

546
00:27:40,220 --> 00:27:41,690
You didn't have to bring

547
00:27:41,710 --> 00:27:43,030
so many things.

548
00:27:43,060 --> 00:27:44,570
Kexian, give it to me.

549
00:27:45,290 --> 00:27:46,050
Yeah.

550
00:27:46,180 --> 00:27:48,380
You two are so thoughtful.

551
00:27:50,680 --> 00:27:51,580
Uncle, Aunt,

552
00:27:51,680 --> 00:27:53,310
I came today because I have something

553
00:27:53,310 --> 00:27:54,240
to ask of you.

554
00:27:54,520 --> 00:27:56,220
What is it? Go ahead.

555
00:27:58,750 --> 00:28:01,590
Ke and I grew up together.

556
00:28:01,910 --> 00:28:02,810
I know her well,

557
00:28:02,980 --> 00:28:03,800
admire her,

558
00:28:05,410 --> 00:28:06,450
and love her.

559
00:28:06,840 --> 00:28:08,850
I want to take care of her
