00:40:28,980 --> 00:40:30,980
his mood must have been much better.

838
00:40:32,040 --> 00:40:33,320
Indeed.

839
00:40:33,770 --> 00:40:37,110
Looks like you also understand
Mr. Lin Yuan's paintings well.

840
00:40:37,110 --> 00:40:38,770
We seem to have much in common.

841
00:40:56,570 --> 00:40:58,480
Today has flown by so quickly.

842
00:40:58,510 --> 00:41:00,160
Appreciating paintings with you

843
00:41:00,160 --> 00:41:01,100
has been delightful.

844
00:41:01,100 --> 00:41:03,060
Being able
to appreciate paintings with you

845
00:41:03,060 --> 00:41:04,460
also makes me very happy.

846
00:41:04,730 --> 00:41:06,030
Am I so happy

847
00:41:06,280 --> 00:41:08,020
because I've seen so many

848
00:41:08,070 --> 00:41:09,310
of Mr. Lin Yuan's paintings?

849
00:41:09,310 --> 00:41:11,910
Or is it because Mr. Huang was the one

850
00:41:12,320 --> 00:41:13,850
appreciating them with me?

851
00:41:14,190 --> 00:41:15,030
Miss Qiyue.

852
00:41:16,290 --> 00:41:17,090
What's wrong?

853
00:41:18,280 --> 00:41:19,320
N-Nothing.

854
00:41:20,860 --> 00:41:23,320
I came to the capital
because of Mr. Lin Yuan.

855
00:41:23,440 --> 00:41:24,720
This happiness

856
00:41:25,180 --> 00:41:26,700
must be because of Mr. Lin Yuan.

857
00:41:26,700 --> 00:41:27,590
Miss Qiyue.

858
00:41:28,820 --> 00:41:29,950
Let's go then.

859
00:41:29,980 --> 00:41:30,570
Okay.

860
00:41:42,190 --> 00:41:42,710
Please.

861
00:41:49,080 --> 00:41:52,050
Mr. Lin Yuan is truly talented.

862
00:41:52,560 --> 00:41:54,210
After seeing so many of his paintings,

863
00:41:54,210 --> 00:41:55,810
I understand him better now.

864
00:41:56,540 --> 00:41:57,600
His loneliness.

865
00:41:58,390 --> 00:41:59,510
His joy.

866
00:42:00,100 --> 00:42:01,230
His inner thoughts.

867
00:42:02,350 --> 00:42:03,610
His open-mindedness.

868
00:42:05,860 --> 00:42:07,620
I must find Mr. Lin Yuan.

869
00:42:16,870 --> 00:42:17,630
Senior.

870
00:42:18,810 --> 00:42:19,910
Your...

871
00:42:20,370 --> 00:42:22,080
Senior, there's no one else here.

872
00:42:22,080 --> 00:42:23,590
No need for such formality.

873
00:42:23,590 --> 00:42:24,000
Sit.

874
00:42:27,100 --> 00:42:28,980
Junior, how have you been lately?

875
00:42:30,940 --> 00:42:32,820
Senior, hearing you call me that

876
00:42:33,100 --> 00:42:35,330
reminds me of the days we trained together

877
00:42:35,330 --> 00:42:36,550
at Mount Qianya.

878
00:42:37,330 --> 00:42:39,860
Mount Qianya is the secret guard post
my father established for me.

879
00:42:39,860 --> 00:42:41,080
We grew up together,

880
00:42:41,550 --> 00:42:42,680
like real brothers.

881
00:42:43,510 --> 00:42:46,620
When my family was destroyed,
my foster father took me in.

882
00:42:46,620 --> 00:42:47,960
He taught the three of us

883
00:42:47,990 --> 00:42:49,740
to respect our master,
treat each other as brothers,

884
00:42:49,740 --> 00:42:52,340
and always uphold
loyalty and righteousness.

885
00:42:53,390 --> 00:42:54,090
Senior,

886
00:42:54,830 --> 00:42:57,030
now the capital is full of hidden risks.

887
00:42:57,050 --> 00:42:58,710
You're the only one I can trust

888
00:42:58,800 --> 00:43:00,260
and rely on.

889
00:43:00,530 --> 00:43:01,330
Rest assured.

890
00:43:01,580 --> 00:43:03,210
I will fight alongside you

891
00:43:03,240 --> 00:43:04,840
to eliminate all obstacles.

892
00:43:06,370 --> 00:43:08,030
You've always been good to me,

893
00:43:08,310 --> 00:43:09,510
but these past years,

894
00:43:09,590 --> 00:43:11,120
you've truly endured much.

895
00:43:11,400 --> 00:43:12,880
You lived in concealment at Mount Qianya.

896
00:43:12,880 --> 00:43:14,280
And I could only
bear the humiliation and wait.

897
00:43:14,280 --> 00:43:15,760
Those vermin corrupting the court—

898
00:43:15,760 --> 00:43:18,490
we must eliminate
every last one of my uncle's men

899
00:43:19,700 --> 00:43:21,590
to end this threat once and for all.

900
00:43:21,590 --> 00:43:24,430
The rise and fall of the nation
concerns every citizen.

901
00:43:24,430 --> 00:43:26,940
I'm duty-bound in this.

902
00:43:27,490 --> 00:43:29,340
Besides, I didn't leave Mount Qianya

903
00:43:29,340 --> 00:43:31,070
solely for official business.

904
00:43:31,330 --> 00:43:33,260
Not solely for official business?

905
00:43:33,720 --> 00:43:36,020
Why haven't I heard you mention it before?

906
00:43:36,020 --> 00:43:36,870
What is it?

907
00:43:37,280 --> 00:43:38,410
I came to the capital

908
00:43:38,740 --> 00:43:40,530
also to find the little girl

909
00:43:41,160 --> 00:43:42,960
who saved my life when I was a kid.

910
00:43:44,940 --> 00:43:46,180
I remember now.

911
00:43:46,310 --> 00:43:48,530
The little girl who gave you desserts

912
00:43:49,160 --> 00:43:51,270
and the gold badge back then.

913
00:43:52,280 --> 00:43:53,660
So, have you found her?

914
00:43:53,820 --> 00:43:55,880
Do you need me to send more men to help?

915
00:43:56,230 --> 00:43:57,160
No need for that.

916
00:43:57,580 --> 00:43:58,910
I've already found her.

917
00:44:02,360 --> 00:44:04,160
So you didn't leave Mount Qianya

918
00:44:04,170 --> 00:44:05,900
just to help solve my problems.

919
00:44:06,010 --> 00:44:08,070
You came for your little girl as well.

920
00:44:09,230 --> 00:44:10,080
Tell me,

921
00:44:10,270 --> 00:44:11,950
am I going to have a sister-in-law soon?

922
00:44:11,950 --> 00:44:14,090
Alright, let's not talk about this now.

923
00:44:14,090 --> 00:44:16,850
I heard you've been departing the palace
frequently these days.

924
00:44:16,850 --> 00:44:18,560
Is it because
Marquis Wu'an has made new moves?
